<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Form Submission</title>
    <style>
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f6f9;
            color: #333;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fdfdfd;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 120px rgba(6, 3, 3, 0.5);
        }

        .email-header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .email-header img {
            width: 175px;
            max-width: 300px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .email-header h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            color: #1a202c; 
            margin: 0;
        }

        .email-body {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #444;
        }

        .email-body h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #1a202c;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .email-body p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #666;
        }

        .email-body ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
            list-style-type: none;
        }

        .email-body ul li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .email-body .message {
            font-style: italic;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #FF5733; 
            color: #fff;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #e04d2b;
        }

        .email-footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #aaa;
        }

        .email-footer a {
            color: #FF5733;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .email-footer p {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <img src="https://exchme.com/images/icons/logo.png" alt="exchme">
            <h1>Contact Form Submission</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="email-body">
            <h2>Hello <%=name%>,</h2>
            <p>We have received a new submission from our <a href="https://exchme.com/">website's</a> contact form. Please find the details below:</p>

            <ul>
                <li><strong>Name:</strong> <%=name%></li>
                <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%=email%></li>
            </ul>

            <p><strong>Message:</strong></p>
            <p class="message"><%=message%></p>

            <p>Thank you for reaching out to us! We will get back to you shortly. If you need any assistance in the meantime, feel free to contact us directly.</p>
            Site: <a href="https://exchme.com/">https://exchme.com/</a>
        </div>
<hr>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us at <a href="mailto:support@exchme.com">support@exchme.com</a>.</p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Exchme. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
